# Cloudflare Pages routing rules.
# Order matters — most specific first.

# 1) The admin SPA shell. Sent to /index.html so React Router takes over.
/admin-tools/*  /index.html  200

# 2) Redirects are dynamically generated from content/seo/redirects.json
#    by scripts/generate-robots.ts (or a future generate-redirects.ts).

# 3) Default SPA fallback for the landing page. NOTE: this MUST be the very last
#    rule. Cloudflare serves prerendered static HTML files (/ru/foo/index.html)
#    automatically before this rule fires, so money/blog pages get their real
#    content, and only unknown paths fall back to the SPA shell.
/*  /index.html  200
